text: Davit Bakradze (; born 1 July 1972) is a Georgian politician and diplomat who was the Chairman of the Parliament of Georgia from June 7, 2008, to October 21, 2012. He is one of the leaders of European Georgia. He was Foreign Minister of Georgia. ==Notes== == References == ==Other websites== *Bakradze - Government of Georgia Website * |- Category:1972 births Category:Politicians from Tbilisi Category:Georgian diplomats Category:Living people Category:Speakers of the Parliament of Georgia
